==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Equanimous
<hw>E*quan"i*mous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>aequanimus</ets>, fr. <ets>aequus</ets> equal + <ets>animus</ets>
mind.]</ety> <def>Of an even, composed frame of mind; of a steady
temper; not easily elated or depressed.</def> <rj><au>Bp.
Gauden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Equant</ent>⟦br⟧
